            "text_bbD7Ej": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>All our designs are original creations by the Sky Goodies team, and are the copyright and perpetual intellectual property of Sky Goodies Products and Applications Private Limited. Sky Goodies is owned and managed by its directors, Amit Gudibanda and Misha Gudibanda. All Sky Goodies’ products are designed by hand with love, in Mumbai, India. Almost all our products are made from FSC certified paper from responsible sources, and are 100% biodegradable. </p><p>To know more about our story, please see these links: <br/> <a href=\"https://yourstory.com/2016/03/sky-goodies/\" target=\"_blank\">https://yourstory.com/2016/03/sky-goodies/</a></p><p>To know more about our philosophy, please see this link: <br/><a href=\"https://www.skygoodies.co/making-and-paper-craft/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.skygoodies.co/making-and-paper-craft/</a></p>",
